5e SRD attribution
------------------

This engine reuses general 5e mechanics (proficiency progression, ability
scores, advantage/disadvantage, save DC arithmetic, the d20 resolution loop,
condition vocabulary, the dual-pool rest/recovery shape, and the standard array)
which are derived from the System Reference Document 5.1 published by Wizards
of the Coast.

