Naruto-specific content (clan rosters, jutsu catalog, chakra natures, KKG
recipes, in-world setting) is fan-authored and is NOT covered by the SRD
license. The Phase A generalization in this engine deliberately separates the
generic 5e-derived rules surface from the Naruto content pack so that the
content can later be replaced by other DLCs without redistributing the Naruto
material.
